data.text:
Yes Minister cast list, including photos of the actors when available. This list includes all of the Yes Minister main actors and actresses, so if they are an integral part of the show you'll find them below. You can various bits of trivia about these Yes Minister stars, such as where the actor was born and what their year of birth is. This cast list of actors from Yes Minister focuses primarily on the main characters, but there may be a few actors who played smaller roles on Yes Minister that are on here as well.

This list features Nigel Hawthorne Derek Fowlds and more.

If you are wondering, "Who are the actors from Yes Minister?" or "Who starred on Yes Minister?" then this list will help you answer those questions.

In most cases you can click on the names of these popular Yes Minister actors and actresses to find out more information about them. If you're looking for a particular Yes Minister actor or actress, then type their name into the "search" bar to find them directly.
